: You can block cookies by activating a setting on your browser allowing you to refuse cookies. You can also delete cookies through your browser settings. If you turn off cookies, you can continue to use the Gaia website, but certain services may not work effectively.
You can opt out of receiving Gaia information
: You have the option to opt out of receiving information from Gaia, the website, and the services. The option to opt out will appear at the bottom of every promotional email that is sent. If you no longer wish to take advantage of the websites or the services or receive any form of direct contact from Gaia, whether email, discounts, newsletters, or other promotion offers or materials, contact us at
info@gaia.com
or call (866)-284-8058.
